<% locals.breadcrumbs = [ {name: 'Home', link: '/'}, {name: project.group.name,
link: `/browse/${project.group.safeName}`}, {name: 'Edit Project', active: true}
]; %> <% include ../head.ejs %>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="title has-text-centered">Edit: <%- project.name %></h1>

    <section class="section">
      <p>
        A <b>Project</b> is pretty much equivalent to a research theme within
        your <b>Research Group</b>. This is the biggest umbrella group and many
        researchers will contribute to a single project. Although you may use
        the word project to refer to one part of your PhD or post-doc, that's
        not how we're using it here. We mean something more at the group level.
        It shouldn't take too many words to come up with a project name. If
        there are existing projects in the database, see whether you can add to
        one rather than creating a new one. As such using your own name as the
        name for a project is a very bad idea! Your group and the research theme
        will very likely outlast your tenure here so please use something
        descriptive. It will help your group in the future.
      </p>
    </section>

    <form method="post" action="/browse/<%- project.group.safeName %>/new">
      <input
        type="hidden"
        name="id"
        value="<%- project.id %>"
        class="is-hidden"
      />

      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="field">
            <label class="label">Project Name</label>
            <div class="control">
              <input
                class="input"
                type="text"
                placeholder="New project name"
                name="name"
                maxlength="30"
                value="<%-project.name %>"
                required
              />
            </div>
            <p class="help">The name of your project</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column">
          <div class="field">
            <label class="label">Short Description</label>
            <div class="control">
              <textarea
                class="input"
                placeholder="Short description"
                name="shortDescription"
                minlength="20"
                maxlength="100"
                required
              >
<%- project.shortDescription  %></textarea
              >
            </div>
            <p class="help">
              a short description of the project. 20-100 characters
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label class="label">Long Description</label>
        <div class="control">
          <textarea
            class="input"
            placeholder="Long description"
            minlength="100"
            name="longDescription"
          >
<%- project.longDescription %></textarea
          >
        </div>
        <p class="help">a long description of the project. 100+ characters</p>
      </div>

      <div class="control">
        <button class="button is-success">Update</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
<% include ../foot.ejs %>
